WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.085
Seventeen seconds. Yeah.
Exactly 1 7 seconds.

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:05.254
-Ladies and gentlemen...
-l'm gonna ask you just to leave.

00:00:05.339 --> 00:00:07.131
lt took exactly 1 7 seconds
for my ex-wife,

00:00:07.215 --> 00:00:09.008
Deana Coleman,
to ask me if l was drinking.

00:00:09.092 --> 00:00:10.968
-Just leave, Will.
-What, is that a world record?

00:00:11.053 --> 00:00:13.262
