00:00:28.528 --> 00:00:30.696
You upset my mother. You gotta go.

00:00:30.781 --> 00:00:32.782
Well, l'm your father, tough guy.

00:00:32.866 --> 00:00:34.283
You're a drunk.

00:00:34.660 --> 00:00:35.660
Get off!

00:00:35.786 --> 00:00:37.953
l'm a drunk. You don't know
who the fuck l am.

00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:40.289
l sure don't! Why don't you tell me?

00:00:40.374 --> 00:00:41.332
What?

00:00:41.416 --> 00:00:43.292
Who the fuck are you? Who are you?

00:00:43.377 --> 00:00:44.543
Get the fuck out!

00:00:46.797 --> 00:00:47.963
